/!  Begin Page Content
section.hero.d-flex
  .container-lg
    .squiggle.mb-5
    .row.justify-content-start.align-items-center
      .col-md-6.col-lg-6
        h1 Cloud Storage Management Web App
        p.lead
        	| Jumpix is a web-based application designed to help users access and move files across major cloud providers through a single, unified platform. The product simplifies file management across multiple cloud accounts and environments, making access easy regardless of where files are stored.
		/ .d-inline.mb-5.mb-md-0
