				p Jumpix
			.col-md-6
				h6 Year
				p 2013 - 2016
        .row.mb-3
			.col-md-6
				h6 Services
				p Strategy, Website Design & Development, UX/UI Design, Graphic Design, Iconography, Media, Email Campaigns
			.col-md-6
